{"word":"G1141 - δαιμονιώδης - daimoniṓdēs - dahee-mon-ee-o'-dace - Devilish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δαιμονιώδης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">daimoniṓdēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dahee-mon-ee-o'-dace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Devilish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பேய்த்தனமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"resembling or proceeding from an evil spirit, demon - like"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1140 - δαιμόνιον - daimónion - dahee-mon'-ee-on/1140\">G1140</a> and <a href=\"#/G1142 - δαίμων - daímōn - dah'-ee-mown/1142\">G1142</a>; <i>daemon like:</i> - devilish.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1139/1139\">G1139</a>, <a href=\"#/G1140/1140\">G1140</a>, <a href=\"#/G1141/1141\">G1141</a>, <a href=\"#/G1142/1142\">G1142</a>"}]}